Additionally, it mentions "Stable release 1.0 / October 24, 2011; 0 days ago ( ) Written in C Operating system FreeRTOS, Linux Type Protocol License GNU Lesser General Public License Website http://www.libcsp.org", confirming the homepage as www.libcsp.org.
